<strong>Blur</strong> = The category view will be blurred for a short period of time when loading.<br>
<strong>Bars</strong> = When loading the category view, a loading animation with bars will be displayed.<br>
<strong>Spinner</strong> = When loading the category view, a loading animation with a spinner will be displayed.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Show category image in category view</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Activate to display a preview image in the category view. The preview image can be uploaded in the <strong>Documents</strong> tab of the category and must be set as image 1.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Show category description in category view</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Activate to display a description in the category view. The description can be entered in the <strong>Description 1</strong> tab of the category.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
