<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Explanation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Last seen: Number of last seen items</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select the number of last seen items.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Cross-selling: Cross-selling relation</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select the relation for cross-selling items. Items with this relation will be displayed in an item list of the <strong>Cross-selling</strong> type.<br>
<strong>Similar</strong> = The selected items are similar to the opened item.<br>
<strong>Accessory</strong> = The selected items are accessories of the opened item.<br>
<strong>Replacement part</strong> = The selected items are replacement parts for the opened item.<br>
<strong>Collection</strong> = The selected items are suitable to be sold as a bundle together with the opened item.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>First item list;<br>
Second item list;<br>
Third item list</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select the type of the item list.<br>
<strong>Last seen</strong> = A list of last seen items is displayed in the online store.<br>
<strong>Cross-selling</strong> = A list of cross-selling items with the selected relation is displayed in the online store.<br>
<strong>Tags</strong> = A list of items of the linked tags is displayed in the online store.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Name of the first item list (DE);<br>
Name of the second item list (DE);<br>
Name of the third item list (DE)</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter the name of the item list for the German online store. This name is optional for item lists of the <strong>Last seen</strong> and <strong>Cross-selling</strong> types.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Name of the first item list (EN);<br>
Name of the second item list (EN);<br>
Name of the third item list (EN)</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter the name of the item list for the English online store. This name is optional for item lists of the <strong>Last seen</strong> and <strong>Cross-selling</strong> type.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>List of IDs of tags to display in the first item list;<br>
List of IDs of tags to display in the second item list;<br>
List of IDs of tags to display in the third item list</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter the IDs of tags to display items linked to these tags in an item list of the <strong>Tags</strong> type.<br>
<strong><em>Note:</em></strong> Multiple IDs must be separated by commas.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
