</table>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="201">1.10. Carrying out settings for search engine optimisation</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the <strong>SEO</strong> tab you find settings for optimising your online store for search engines. Enter a meta description for the static pages of your online store, for example, and control access to your online store pages by robots.</p>
</div>
<div id="202" class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Carrying out settings for search engine optimisation:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Plugins » Plugin overview</strong>.<br>
→ The plugin overview will open.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Ceres</strong>.<br>
→ The plugin will open.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Configuration</strong> in the directory tree.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>SEO</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-seo-settings">Table 11</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
